officer direction and feedback to members of the creative department Creative Director requirements This section should list the essential qualities of an ideal candidate. Include previous work experience, education or achievements that would be beneficial. And list any preferred hard and soft skills. Example Creative Director requirements Bachelor\u2019s degree in graphic design, marketing or related field 5+ years experience as a creative director or management position Proven history of success in leadership roles A strong portfolio of successful creative projects Solid understanding of design and marketing best practices Skilled communicator and team player Creative Director related job titles: Art Director Manage, Creative Marketing Social Art Director Associate Director of Marketing Director, Digital Marketing & Creative Services Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
